Murray & Roberts Says Clough Sells Marine Construction Unit to SapuraCrest

-- B y   A l a s t a i r   R e e d
-- 
2011-08-08T07:59:03Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-08-08/murray-roberts-says-clough-sells-marine-construction-unit-to-sapuracrest.html
Murray & Roberts Holdings Ltd. (MUR)  said
its 62 percent-owned Australian listed unit,  Clough Ltd. (CLO) , has
agreed to sell its offshore marine construction business to
 SapuraCrest Petroleum Bhd. (SCRES)   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Alastair Reed at 
 areed12@bloomberg.net  